<html><head><base href="{{settings.SITE.server_url}}" target="_blank"></head><body>
<body>
<p>Dear {{obj.get_full_name()}},</p>

<p>Welcome to the
<a href="{{rt.settings.SITE.server_url}}">{{rt.settings.SITE.server_url}}</a> site.
</p>

{% if obj.verification_code %}
{% set expiry = settings.SITE.plugins.users.verification_code_expires %}
Please {{tostring(ar.row_action_button(obj,
    rt.models.users.Me.get_action_by_name('verify'),
    "click here to verify", request_kwargs=dict(action_param_values=dict(
    email=obj.email, verification_code=obj.verification_code))))}}.
Or verify using your verificataion code: <b>{{obj.verification_code}}</b> from
the browser application.
<p>Your verification code will expire in <span><b>
    {% if expiry / 60 > 1 %}{{expiry / 60}} hours.
    {% else %}{{expiry}} minutes.
    {% endif %}</b></span></p>
{% endif %}

<p>Thank you for joining us.</p>

</body>
